== Overview ==
The ADVI Deflection Grid is one of the most significant defensive enhancements available. Whilst difficult to keep powered up, the grid is capable of deflecting energy weapons damage to shields.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Deflection Grid can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
